pageTitle: Summer meal program to provide meals | GrantKY.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {19151=Grant County Schools will participate in a Summer Feeding Program during the months of June and July. If you belong to a local organization that would like to participate in the program, call to reserve a spot. The Grant County School system has the right to accept or refuse locations based on attendance or availability. The deadline to sign up is April 30. Call 859-824-2875 to setup a location, time of meal service, average attendance and dates of needed service., 24722=The Grant County News | circulation@grantky.com | 859-824-3343 129 South Main Street, Dry Ridge, KY 41035 Office Hours are 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m., Monday through Friday, 31577=Copyright © 2015}
